{"tid":2274793,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(估地方) 唐狗身中多刀  傷口見骨雙目恐失明","createTime":"2020-11-06T16:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T04:11:44.000Z","uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c46ff94e1a701a90205a8c094d2c3722e4fd0745","tid":2274793,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"【虐待動物】虐狗狂徒斬唐狗多刀  傷口深至見骨  眼球跌出恐失明<br />\n<br />\n今日 (6日) 警方接獲「毛孩守護者」義工報案指，元朗八鄉錦上路上村一隻黑色約5歲唐狗疑被刀斬傷，額頭傷口深至見骨淌血，左眼眼球幾乎跌出眼眶，頸部被綠色繩及白色電線捆綁。受傷唐狗被義工送往動物診所進行手術，目前未有生命危險，但有機會失明。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查，案件列殘酷對待動物，交由元朗警區刑事調查隊第九隊調查，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日連接發生多宗虐待動物案件，香港非牟利獸醫診所主席麥志豪表示，律政司放生虐待動物的兇徒，使社會上出現愈來愈多「變態者」，犯罪後不用付上代價。<br />\n<br />\n資料片段來源：Facebook走失協尋 (狗/貓) 群組<br />\n========================= <br />\n🚚丘品購物網站正式上線啦「丘MART」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.yaumart.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yaumart.com%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=b46429ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.yaumart.com/</a> <br />\n========================= <br />\n感謝讀者支持 支持新聞部課金方法 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3579Rub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3579Rub&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=abb2ed1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3579Rub</a> <br />\n=========================<br />\n丘品已經登陸Patreon 歡迎成為會員&rdquo;搶先收睇 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/cupidproducer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fcupidproducer&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=68e905c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/cupidproducer</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; <br />\n📣Instagram : <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LShtZr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LShtZr&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6Vn